    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine, flawless condition. Not a scratch on it, the interior still has that fresh feel, and it drives like an absolute dream! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
