    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, recently enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service binder detailing every oil change and inspection performed at authorized dealerships. With a spotless undercarriage and a factory-fresh engine bay, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its model year. It is a turn-key collector's piece ready for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 43800.0,
