      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been tucked away in a garage its whole life. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a home with someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
