      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2017 Shelby GT350, preserved in collector-grade condition. This unit features the high-revving 5.2L Voodoo V8 with its signature flat-plane crankshaft, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,250 RPM redline. Power is managed via a TREMEC TR-3160 6-speed manual and a 3.73 Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with the MagneRide Damping System for precise lateral dynamics, complemented by Brembo 6-piston fixed front calipers and cross-drilled rotors for optimal thermal management. Zero modifications; factory-spec throughout with documented service intervals and impeccable paint depth.",
